168
00:16:45,993 --> 00:16:48,627
<i>- Xin lỗi!
- Đừng đi!</i>

169
00:16:48,629 --> 00:16:51,964
<i>Giúp tao! Đừng đi!</i>

170
00:16:53,967 --> 00:16:57,001
