- Đón Hershel.</i>

171
00:16:57,003 --> 00:16:59,237
<i>Giúp tôi với!</i>

172
00:16:59,239 --> 00:17:01,572
<i>- Đừng!
- Her ... Hershel!</i>

173
00:17:01,574 --> 00:17:04,808


174
00:17:26,798 --> 00:17:29,233
Hershel. Hershel.

175
00:17:33,806 --> 00:17:36,474
